flowchart TD

    A[Admin opens Assessment menu] --> B[System shows Assessment List]

    B --> C{Choose action}

    %% Preview
    C -->|Preview| D[Open Assessment Preview]
    D --> E[Show simulation of assessment flow]
    E --> F[Admin reviews simulated questions and result flow]
    F --> B

    %% View Results
    C -->|View Results| G[Open Assessment Results List]
    G --> H{Any completed results?}
    H -->|No| I[Show empty state]
    H -->|Yes| J[Show all completed user results]

    %% Result Detail
    J --> K[Admin selects one result]
    K --> L[Open Result Detail]
    L --> M[Show summary: name email phone correct answers points percentage duration]
    M --> N[Show all questions and user answers]
    N --> O[Back to Results]
    O --> J

    %% Delete Result
    J --> P[Admin clicks Delete result]
    P --> Q[Show delete confirmation]
    Q --> R{Confirm delete?}
    R -->|No| J
    R -->|Yes| S[Delete selected result]
    S --> T[Refresh results list]
    T --> J

    %% Edit/Delete Assessment
    C -->|Edit| U[Open Assessment Edit]
    U --> B

    C -->|Delete| V[Delete Assessment Flow]
    V --> B